{"tid":2518243,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返工屙屎地方放埋啲小盆栽其實係咪就係班HR 嘅傑作？","createTime":"2021-05-06T01:36:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-06T05:52:13.000Z","uid":40930,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3a8f03296cb8b5e7308f0825ef281ebb30fa200c","tid":2518243,"uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T01:36:32.000Z","msg":"每日返工都會屙屎，所以去親屙屎就好似返屋企咁，因為你每日都會返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bus.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我每日去屙屎個陣都留意到個廁所會放咗啲小盆栽<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但其實放埋啲咁嘅嘢嚮廁所有乜用？屙屎會順利啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n極度懷疑呢啲就係公司班所謂HR 諗出嚟嘅屎橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地平時冇嘢做，又冇嘢叻，就諗埋啲咁嘅鳩橋出嚟扮到事無大小都為公司出一分力<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你用埋啲鳩錢放落去啲鳩嘢到，點解唔用筆錢買下嘢食請人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/wa.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n起碼食完又可以去屙多一轉屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n放舊咁嘅嘢係廁所又唔食得，究竟有冇腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997433982acb9c3259a524a07b28862f93708280","tid":2518243,"uid":262358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3a8f03296cb8b5e7308f0825ef281ebb30fa200c","tid":2518243,"uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T01:36:32.000Z","msg":"每日返工都會屙屎，所以去親屙屎就好似返屋企咁，因為你每日都會返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bus.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我每日去屙屎個陣都留意到個廁所會放咗啲小盆栽<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但其實放埋啲咁嘅嘢嚮廁所有乜用？屙屎會順利啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n極度懷疑呢啲就係公司班所謂HR 諗出嚟嘅屎橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地平時冇嘢做，又冇嘢叻，就諗埋啲咁嘅鳩橋出嚟扮